news.summary: SANTA CLARA, Calif., Nov. 04, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- AMD (NASDAQ:AMD) today announced financial results for the third quarter of 2025. news.title: Viswanathan Anand Inaugurates Tech Mahindra's First-of-Its-Kind Global Chess League Experience Center in Dallas
news.summary: Tech Mahindra (NSE: TECHM), a leading global provider of technology consulting and digital solutions to enterprises across industries, has launched the Global Chess League (GCL) Experience Center at its U.S. headquarters in Plano, Dallas. Viswanathan Anand, five-time World Chess Champion, inaugurated the center, marking a significant milestone in Tech Mahindra's mission to combine technology, innovation, and the spirit of chess.
